import * as React from 'react'
import { Text ,View,Button,Image} from 'react-native'

export default function HomeScreen({navigation}) {
    return (
    	<>
    	<Button
      title="SignIn Our DataBase For More Offers"
      onPress={() =>
        navigation.navigate('SignIn')}
    />
        <View>
                <Text>HomeScreen</Text>
                <Image source={{uri:"https://www.google.com/search?q=innocent+sticks&rlz=1C1CHBD_enLK881LK881&sxsrf=ALeKk000GnKAjCMpxWYRutmLhN0CQOqlIg:1602509325555&tbm=isch&source=iu&ictx=1&fir=c_Sv5btvC4tt9M%252CuP4LhcsiBQB8WM%252C_&vet=1&usg=AI4_-kTfYtRTywYbu0LVpit3hGcrCxA1lw&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwji--S4lK_sAhXjjOYKHVGlDjgQ9QF6BAgKEB0#imgrc=c_Sv5btvC4tt9M"}}/>
        </View>
        </>
    )
}
